  "description": "This individual is an undead human of indeterminate age, preserved in the cavern’s dry air with light skin pulled tight over prominent cheekbones and a narrow jaw. Gray eyes sit deep in darkened sockets, fixed in a watchful, unblinking stare that reinforces an impression of tireless vigilance. Black hair hangs in long, uneven lengths, with thinning at the temples that exposes a high, bony brow. The hands are sinew-thin and rigid, the fingers permanently curled as if set by long-ago cramps into a grasping posture.",
